          Shannon Chan-Kent
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-3xl text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg 2xl:text-lg leading-snug sm:leading-normal text-white text-left">
          Shannon has been in the film/tv/voice over industry for nearly 20 years. She is a trained opera singer holding a BMUS and MMUS in Opera Performance from the University of British Columbia. A few of Shannon's VO credits include <i>My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic</i> (series and feature), <i>Gigantosaurus</i>, <i>Polly Pocket</i>, <i>Corner Gas: The Animated Series</i>, <i>Slugterra</i>, <i>DeathNote</i>, <i>16 Hudson</i>, <i>The Bravest Knight</i>, <i>Mega Man</i> and <i>Hello Ninja</i>. Film and tv credits include <i>Life Sentence</i> (CW), <i>Another Life</i> (Netflix), <i>Good Trouble</i> (Hulu/Freeform) and <i>You</i> (Netflix). Shannon is also no stranger to the live stage. She has been in productions such as <i>Beauty And The Beast</i> (Belle), <i>Avenue Q</i>, <i>Evita</i>, <i>The Magic Flute</i> and <i>The Flick</i>.
        </div>
      </div>
